            </li>
            <br>
            <li>
              Chemical Records: Digitize your chemical records and enjoy complete
              control of your data to begin analyzing trends.
            </li>
            <br>
            <li>
              Employee Management: Track all relevant information about your staff.
            </li>
            <br>
            <li>
              Help Desk: Track all of your maintance issues in the cloud.
            </li>
            <br>
            <li>
              Slide Inspections: Handle your daily slide inspections directly
              from the app, automatically receive an email if any probelms arise.
            </li>
        </div>
      </center>
      <br>
      <strong id='info-header'> Get started in under 5 minutes today. </strong>
      <center>
        <p style='width: 375px;'>
          Bring your pool into the 21st century by following our quick and easy
          sign up process. Keep those filing cabniets closed and begin managing
          your data and workforce in the cloud immediately.
        </p>
      </center>
